{
  "stem": "8423.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my Bubbe, as we called her, was very busy in the field.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she more or less let us run loose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And also, we learned Ukraine, which was very good-- Ukraine from the Ukraine people who lived there, who were Russian Orthodox, and Yiddish from my grandmother, because we didn't speak Yiddish in the house.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And even though Grandma could speak a perfect Hungarian, she would pretend not to understand a word if we spoke in Hungarian, just so we would speak to her in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we actually learned two languages while we were there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we learned German in the school, a little German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had German, Hungarian, Ukraine, and Yiddish at that point.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was Bubbe Rosner?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, my mother's mother, my maternal grandmother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she had the biggest influence on me, I think, in my life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, in my books that I have written, I speak mostly about Bubbe, which is sort of strange, especially the first book.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think because she was so different.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was strict in her own way, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she was very religious, so very different from my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she always talked about God.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she just presented life to us in a very different way then we ever saw anybody else in the city, you know, believe and do.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And her morals were just so strict.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she was always there for her neighbors, helping to deliver children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I mean this for the Christian neighbors as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They all loved her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If somebody was sick, she was like the medicine lady, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would call on her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she always knew what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Usually we took turns because Grandma was a widow.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
